36
0:01:44.16,000 --> 0:01:46,000
First, about a guy named Nathan Winograd.

37
0:01:46.16,000 --> 0:01:5,000
Nathan was the number two person at the San Francisco SPCA.

38
0:01:50.16,000 --> 0:01:52,000
