96
0:04:27.16,000 --> 0:04:29,000
or power to lever a system,

97
0:04:29.16,000 --> 0:04:31,000
but by leading.

98
0:04:31.16,000 --> 0:04:34,000
So let me tell you about the three cycles. The first one is the factory cycle.

99
0:04:34.16,000 --> 0:04:38,000
