105
0:04:48.16,000 --> 0:04:5,000
you can churn out a lot of cars.

106
0:04:50.16,000 --> 0:04:53,000
You can make a lot of change. You can get roads built.

107
0:04:53.16,000 --> 0:04:56,000
You can change the fabric of an entire country.

108
0:04:56.16,000 --> 0:04:58,000
That the essence of what you're doing is you need

109
0:04:58.16,000 --> 0:05:,000
ever-cheaper labor,

110
0:05:00.16,000 --> 0:05:03,000
and ever-faster machines.

111
0:05:03.16,000 --> 0:05:06,000
And the problem we've run into is, we're running out of both.

112
0:05:06.16,000 --> 0:05:09,000
Ever-cheaper labor and ever-faster machines.

